            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Pretty difficult to learn steering wheel. Especially because on wheel auto counter-steer defaults to off. Look up a guide on how to actually tune your car on YT. Don't just follow someone elses tune because you need to learn how to play with the tune for different tracks. Once you get a good tune and a good guide to start learning, this game can easily take over your life."
